<paragraph pageId="0" pageNumber="19">Distribution.</paragraph>
<paragraph pageId="0" pageNumber="19">Native in Chongqing (Nanchuan) and Hubei (Yichang) of China. As an economically important fruit, this species has been widely cultivated in central &amp; south China, as well as in Japan, Korea, India, and some countries in Southeast Asia.</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
